<Panels>
  <config><![CDATA[{
  "published": true,
  "game_id": 73,
  "created_at": "2025-07-22T17:32:19.000Z",
  "level_num": "custom",
  "user_id": 18603,
  "properties": {
    "encrypted": "false",
    "offer_browser_tts": "false",
    "panels": [
      {
        "text": "A **Privacy Engineer** protects **confidentiality**, which means keeping private information secret and safe.\n\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/2572849d9d043eb54fa4f50731aaf7f2-CIA Careers (2).png",
        "key": "test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level3-6ea9678a-ce7e-41b9-abb2-d878eb87ac30",
        "typing": false,
        "fadeInOverPrevious": false
      },
      {
        "text": "They stop personal info from being seen by the wrong people. If **confidentiality** is broken, private data can leak, and that can cause big problems like **data breaches** and **legal trouble**.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/2572849d9d043eb54fa4f50731aaf7f2-CIA Careers (2).png",
        "key": "test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level3-91f6e938-059e-4b97-b572-350b4fa8bbb8",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true,
        "layout": "text-bottom-right"
      },
      {
        "text": "A **Forensics Analyst** helps protect **integrity**, which means making sure information hasn’t been changed or messed with.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/d0e036e1613173ad40aa760cbe9dd850-CIA Careers (3).png",
        "key": "test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson6-level3-dc7c3b55-aff2-4031-bd63-72f96c8c4e50",
        "layout": "text-top-left"
      },
      {
        "text": "They look for signs that something was changed in a sneaky or incorrect way. If **integrity** is lost, it could lead to **misinformation** or even **fraud**.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/d0e036e1613173ad40aa760cbe9dd850-CIA Careers (3).png",
        "key": "test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson6-level3-475200d8-f187-48e4-950b-441088553dcd",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true,
        "layout": "text-bottom-left"
      },
      {
        "text": "A **Site Reliability Engineer** works to protect **availability**, which means making sure systems and websites are always up and working.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/7008cc8d4dad5584a3315bfc4f652410-CIA Careers (4).png",
        "key": "test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson6-level3-badbb4fb-41c9-4df5-98ff-d8eb03fff8a5"
      },
      {
        "text": "They help prevent crashes or slowdowns. If **availability** fails, important tools or services could stop working, causing **lost time** and **missed work**.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/7008cc8d4dad5584a3315bfc4f652410-CIA Careers (4).png",
        "key": "test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson6-level3-25f01c77-e1f2-4704-a744-6095c8d40a84",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true,
        "layout": "text-bottom-right"
      }
    ]
  },
  "audit_log": "[{\"changed_at\":\"2025-07-22T17:32:19.880+00:00\",\"changed\":[\"cloned from \\\"test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level3\\\"\"],\"cloned_from\":\"test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level3\"},{\"changed_at\":\"2025-07-22 17:32:23 +0000\",\"changed\":[],\"changed_by_id\":1574,\"changed_by_email\":\"ken.akiha@code.org\"},{\"changed_at\":\"2025-07-22 18:49:36 +0000\",\"changed\":[\"panels\"],\"changed_by_id\":1574,\"changed_by_email\":\"ken.akiha@code.org\"},{\"changed_at\":\"2025-07-22 19:01:00 +0000\",\"changed\":[\"panels\"],\"changed_by_id\":1574,\"changed_by_email\":\"ken.akiha@code.org\"},{\"changed_at\":\"2025-07-22 22:28:27 +0000\",\"changed\":[\"panels\"],\"changed_by_id\":1574,\"changed_by_email\":\"ken.akiha@code.org\"}]"
}]]></config>
